curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/11845' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM42512", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM42512 is an integrated driver IC for driving  motors and coils in industrial applications. The PH and  EN/FAULT pins allow simple interfacing to controller  circuits.  Internal protection functions are provided for under-  voltage lockout (UVLO), over-current protection (OCP)  and  over-temperature  protection  (OTP).  Fault  conditions are indicated by the EN/FAULT pin.  The SGM42512 is available in a Green TSOT-23-6  package. It operates over an ambient temperature  range of -40℃ to +125℃.        "}'
